{"type":"message","id":"68babd70","parentId":"ea51f1c4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:53:06.534Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-04-02 20:53 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 执行自主学习任务，搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态：\n\n1. 搜索关键词：企业数字化转型最新政策/动态、智能安防行业趋势、网络系统集成动态、IT运维服务行业趋势\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 将结果保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n文件格式要求：\n- 第一行：# 行业动态学习笔记\n- 第二行：更新时间：2026-04-02 20:52\n- 接下来是整理的关键信息，每条包含：标题、来源、摘要、关键洞察"}],"timestamp":1775134386531}}
{"type":"message","id":"f628a796","parentId":"68babd70","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:53:11.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to search for industry trends related to 道简网络's business: enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services. Let me search for these topics using the web search skill.","thinkingSignature":"5735295079f19ac7d463c19a8a5024673ab588fc075b1e255b10b64527c5da71"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iqxfpyr1rexp_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42165,"totalTokens":42365,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0000996,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0050598,"total":0.0051944999999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775134386532}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5e569fc","parentId":"f628a796","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:53:11.432Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iqxfpyr1rexp_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775134391429}}
